 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1. Installation
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 
 To run this software, perform the following:
 
 1. Run "make" in the root directory of the project.
 2. Run tstream2jpeg  with the following usage:
 	
 		tstream2jpeg pathToOutputFile pathToJPEGFolder	
 
